content:
The accounts payable balance as at 30 September 2022 mainly entailed management consulting fees to 企業管理諮詢公司 of CNY2.3M and logistics services fees to 物流發展有限公司 of CNY8.3M

SUMMARY: Used entities '企業管理諮詢公司' (CNY2.3M) and '物流發展有限公司' (CNY8.3M), which constitute the majority of the total accounts payable of CNY11.8M.
